                            <comment id="13488553" author="fmeschbe" created="Thu, 1 Nov 2012 08:39:51 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Committed the patch in Rev. 1404499&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This removes uninstalled bundles from the set of bundles to handle.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Another cause for an IllegalStateException thrown from acquiring the bundle lock is failure to get the lock. In this case the bundle remains in the set and is retried later.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
